  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK471">
<l>viṉaivaliyun taṉvaliyu māṟṟāṉ valiyun</l>
<l>tuṇaivaliyun tūkkic ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (one) weigh well the strength of the deed (he purposes to do), his own strength, the strength of his enemy, and the strength of the allies (of both), and then let him act.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
